      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am seriously so excited to show you this absolute gem! It has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch, smudge, or speck of dust to be found! If you\u2019ve been hunting for that perfect, 'fresh-from-the-factory' feel, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself; you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
