    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in front-midship engineering. This specimen features the 13B-REW rotary engine with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger system intact and functioning with factory-spec boost pressures. The chassis maintains a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by an all-aluminum double-wishbone suspension that minimizes unsprung weight for surgical handling. Every component, from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the short-throw five-speed synchros, operates with tactile precision. This is a zero-modification example with a pristine undercarriage and documented thermal management maintenance, representing the pinnacle of 1990s Japanese performance dynamics.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
